title: NYX PROFESSIONAL MAKEUP
subtitle: Ultimate Shadow Palette
text: This eyeshadow palette features 40   stunning creamy eyeshadows in matte and metallic finishes that instantly conjure up a sumptuous nirvana of super-saturated electric greens and subtle pastels coexisting in a peaceful state of colorfully coordinated chaos. Whatever your version of paradise looks like, this eyeshadow palette is as close to perfection as you can get.
